[EN-US]
This extension will help you to have a better performance and productivity within the platform: New Relic (https://one.newrelic.com/).
You will have access to all the Documentation of: NRQL and Data Dictionary.

With this extension you will be able to learn and develop queries more easily, you will be able to mark (markdown) any element and use the entire Data Dictionary anywhere on the platform.

This extension is customizable, you can customize some settings.

In case of any problems, make a report.
Info.: Monthly Updates
